name: Edition 4/22 tarot card - The Empress
description:
Size: 2362 x 4725 px
This edition card will be released every 4 days.
 
If you are the people who are living a fulfilled life in every way, it's time to know that you are worthy! The Empress will make you aware of the blessings you have and will have created a peaceful and nurturing environment around you. She will help you so that things will work well.

The Empress is depicted as someone who is pregnant, wearing a diadem with 12 stars (representing the zodiac and her dominance over the year). She also wearing a pearl necklace and has a scepter in her hand with an orb at the top which is representative of her power over life. She is sitting with a red pillow (symbol of comfort and sensuality) among a field of the ripe wheat crop (a symbol of abundance) and the trees around her show peace and serenity.

The Empress is the third of Major Arcana, someone who is warm, loving, and charismatic. She is an embodiment of true mother-nature.
 
*This item is available only as a Non-Fungible Token (NFT). It’s strictly prohibited to steal and reduplicate this NFT item.
